casebody.data:
GUTTROFF, Appellant, v. WALLACH et al., Respondents. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 10, 1894.) Appeal from city court, general term. Action by George Guttroff against Julius Wallach and Joseph C. Wallach..

Argued before BOOKSTAVER, BISCHOFF, and PRYOR, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, with costs. See 22 N. Y. Supp. 745.
